dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: I'M REALLY NERVOUS ABOUT THIS PRESENTATION FOR THE BIG BOSS. GOT ANY TIPS FOR ME?

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: REMEMBER TO BRING A BUNCH OF COINS TO JANGLE SELF-CONSCIOUSLY IN YOUR POCKETS.

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: ...AVOID EYE CONTACT AND DON'T PAUSE TO EXPLAIN YOUR ACRONYMS.

dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: I WISH I COULD TELL WHEN YOU'RE KIDDING.
